{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "姜断弦遭到牧羊儿与田灵子的联手刺杀。二人精密配合——田灵子娇小身躯承载牧羊儿，体重身高与常人无异，令姜断弦误判为一人。姜断弦一刀斩断田灵子腰部，牧羊儿趁机以血影长鞭卷喉攻击，却被姜断弦以口咬鞭、刀柄握梢的奇招制服。牧羊儿果断弃鞭，踏影子之肩逃入黑暗。\n\n战后姜断弦与影子展开深谈。影子坦言自己不杀姜断弦，并揭示了一个惊天秘密：他就是以诗、书、画三绝名动士林的眉山先生顾横波。这位姑苏世家子暗中化身江湖最传奇的杀手，如今决定让影子与顾横波同时消失。姜断弦追问雇主身份，顾横波透露雇主是柳伴伴——一个奇怪而美丽的女人，但已落入牧羊儿手中，此后恐将不复为人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你为什么还没有走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "我为什么要走？你刚才出手那一刀，我这一辈子恐怕再也见不到第二次了，你就算杀了我，我也不会走的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你知道我不会杀你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "大概有一点知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "我又不想杀你，你怎么会杀我？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "不错，你的确不想杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "在刚才那一瞬间，你好像根本已经忘了这里有我这样一个人存在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "因为我根本就不是一个人，只不过是个影子而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "我想你现在大概已经相信，影子是从来都不会杀人的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "你不是他们的影子，他们才是你的影子。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "这句话我听不懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "每个人都会有想要杀人的时候，可是每个人杀人的原因和目的都不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "无论他们的杀人动机是什么，都绝对是出于人类最原始的共同需要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "从这些杀人者的身上，你已经看到你自己的心里强暴冲动无知和脆弱的一面，你要杀人的时候，就可以控制住自己了，因为他们的行动已经替你消除了心里的杀机。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "换句话说，他们已经替你把人杀了，你自己又何必再去杀人？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "所以你才会说，我不是他们的影子，他们才是我的影子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_ying_zi",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zi",
      "speaker_name": "影子",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "现在我真听懂这句话的意思了。这句活说得真好。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "text": "等一等。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "text": "我会让你走的，可是你也应该先让我明白一些事。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖花老人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "text": "你究竟是谁？你的身份，你的武功，你的名字，你在没有易名改扮前老得是什么样子，这些事我都想知道。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖花老人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "姜先生，我一直认为你是位君子，一位君子好像是不该试探别人隐私的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖花老人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "而且你自己好像也有两种身份，我相信姜断弦一定不愿别人刺探他有关彭十三豆的秘密。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "text": "我不是君子，不过我至少还可以算是个很讲理的人。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖花老人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "一个讲理的人和君子已经很接近了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "text": "那么你能不能告诉一个很接近君子的人你的贵姓大名？经过了这些事之后，我至少应该知道你的名字。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖花老人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "你还想知道什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "text": "一个'五'字之后再加四个零并不是个小数目，牧羊儿和田灵子价钱也不便宜。谁肯花这么多钱来杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖花老人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "姜先生，我想你一定也知道，如果我泄漏了雇主的秘密，以后就再也不会有人花钱雇我了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖花老人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "这不但有关我的信誉和存折，而且影响到我的原则。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖花老人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "你想知道的两件事，本来我都不该告诉你。但是我却可以为你破例一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "卖花老人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "因为从今以后，影子就会完全消失了。顾横波也一样！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "text": "顾横波？你说的是不是那位以'诗、书、画'三绝名动士林的眉山先生？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "speaker_name": "顾横波",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "text": "他为什么会忽然的消失？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "speaker_name": "顾横波",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "因为顾横波就是我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "text": "那么你是不是说，眉山先生这个人也将要从此消失了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "speaker_name": "顾横波",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "text": "这实在是件很可惜的事。这件事我也许根本就不该问的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "speaker_name": "顾横波",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "你已经问了，我也回答。这些事现在已不重要。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "text": "你那位雇主呢？像你这种人，为什么会泄漏他的秘密？难道他也会消失？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "speaker_name": "顾横波",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "他不会。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "speaker_name": "顾横波",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "可是不管他以前是个什么样的人，以后他都不会再见人了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "speaker_name": "顾横波",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "因为他现在大概已经落入牧羊儿手里。无论谁落入牧羊儿手里，以后都不会再是一个人了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "speaker_name": "姜断弦",
      "listener": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "text": "以前呢，以前他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_heng_bo",
      "speaker_name": "顾横波",
      "listener": "char_jiang_duan_xian",
      "text": "她是个很奇怪的女人，也是个很美丽的女人。她的名字叫柳伴伴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 301
    }
  ],
